code: @Test public void contextLoads() {     ResponseEntity<String> entity = this.restTemplate.getForEntity("/test/hello", String.class).     assertThat(entity.getStatusCode()).isEqualTo(HttpStatus.OK). }
@Bean public TestApplication testApplication() {     return new TestApplication(). }
@Bean public ResourceConfig conf(TestApplication app) {     ResourceConfig config = ResourceConfig.forApplication(app).     config.register(TestController.class).     return config. }
